        "description": "<p>Lists the last commented posts. You can configure how many posts should be displayed.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin files to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/basic-recent-commented-posts</code> directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; screen in WordPress</li>\n<li>To add the widget, go to Appearance -&gt; Widgets, and find the &#8216;Better Recent Comments&#8217; widget in the list, then add to any widget area.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>2.2</h4>\n<p>Removed Dashicon dependency.</p>\n<h4>1.9</h4>\n<p>Simpler style</p>\n<h4>1.7</h4>\n<p>Added Dashicons</p>\n<h4>1.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>better markup for more styling options.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>new translations, better wording, pingbacks are excluded</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed bugs in query.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<p>Initial release.</p>\n"
    },
